text: Impetigore (; lit. Woman of the Damned Land) is a 2019 Indonesian horror thriller movie directed by Joko Anwar and starring Tara Basro, Marissa Anita, Asmara Abigail, Christine Hakim, Ario Bayu, Teuku Rifnu Wikana. ==Filming== The movie was filmed in the villages around Malang, Gempol, Lumbang, Bromo, Lumajang, Ijen, and Banyuwangi. ==Other websites== * * Category:2019 horror movies Category:2019 thriller movies Category:2010s horror thriller movies Category:Indonesian movies Category:South Korean movies Category:American horror thriller movies Category:Movies directed by Joko Anwar
title: Impetigore
